---
layout: base.njk
title: Questions — nationalconversations.orgs
description: The major questions we need to ask about digital society, the economy, and the state.
permalink: /questions/
---

<main class="page-main">
  <div class="container">
    <h1 class="page-title">Questions</h1>
    <p class="page-intro">
      The national conversation starts with clear questions. Explore the core issues across society,
      the private sector, and the public realm.
    </p>
    <div class="row g-4">
      {% for topic in questionTopics %}
      <div class="col-12 col-xl-4">
        <article class="card event-card h-100">
          <div class="card-body d-flex flex-column">
            <h2 class="card-title h4">{{ topic.title }}</h2>
            <p class="card-text text-muted mb-3">{{ topic.intro }}</p>

            <div class="flex-grow-1">
              {% for section in topic.sections %}
                {% if section.heading %}
                <h3 class="h6 text-uppercase text-muted mt-3 mb-2">{{ section.heading }}</h3>
                {% endif %}
                <ul class="mb-3">
                  {% for question in section.questions %}
                  <li class="mb-2">{{ question }}</li>
                  {% endfor %}
                </ul>
              {% endfor %}
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>
      </div>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>
</main>